# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),  
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

---

## [1.0.0] - To be added

### Added
- Introduced initial public release of `django_auth_recovery_codes`.
- Is a Django app that extends any Django application and provides a robust system for generating, storing, and managing **2FA recovery codes**
- Allows users to login using their 2FA Recovery backup code